      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是Infra_WorkerNode，先进入Still状态。那这个Still状态能往哪转？我假设它可能需要接收流量，或者开始执行任务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Moving"
