      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Still有两个去向：一是连到Infra_IngressController，表示节点就绪可以接入流量；二是变成Moving状态，表示开始执行实际工作负载。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
